QuevedoMP — License (PLACEHOLDER)
=================================

The licensing model for QuevedoMP is NOT YET FINALIZED.

The specification proposes a dual-license model (AGPL + commercial), following the
Tesseract/Qt precedent, but the exact terms — including what "commercial" includes and the
implications of any (L)GPL dependencies — are an open decision (see QuevedoMP-SPEC.md §12 and
the build plan's deferred ADR on licensing).

Until that decision is ratified and a real license text is committed here, treat this software
as: All rights reserved, no license granted. Do not redistribute.

